---
title: SuperQuick Double Mushroom Ravioli with Garlic Toasts
description: This super-easy and super-quick veggie-packed supper comes together in a flash! The crusty garlic toasts are perfect for scraping up the Parmesan cream sauce at the bottom of your bowl.

